        "mainbody": "'''Half-oni''' were the offspring of an [[oni]] and another [[humanoid]] creature.\n\nMale oni were known to sometimes take [[human]] females as brides.\n\nWhen [[ogre]]s and [[oni magi]] bred, the resulting half-oni eventually developed into a new race of [[ogrima]].\n\nHalf-oni could also be produced through magical means, as occurred in the town of [[Kudoku]], when the [[wu jen]] geisha [[Namiko Li]] began using dark rituals to transform herself and her servants into oni."
